---
title: Chilli-Butter Halloumi, Chicken & Garden Salad with Tomato, Herby Mayonnaise & Flaked Almonds
description: Golden, crispy halloumi and chicken meets a spicy kick in this hearty vegetarian salad! Paired with crisp veg, crunchy almonds, and a luscious drizzle of herby mayo, it’s a fresh, fiery, and oh-so-satisfying dish. Get ready for a salad that steals the spotlight!
